{"tid":225124,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗晚餐 - 美國辣肉腸香蒜黑椒磨菇蛋黃醬熱狗","createTime":"2017-05-01T14:13:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T18:12:22.000Z","uid":74981,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"963f62ae5fa22b06d81831565c54348181e20a1a","tid":225124,"uid":74981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/11e9f71bae2432f07691346861550d6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F11e9f71bae2432f07691346861550d6a.jpg&h=4789bcd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片如下:<br />\n<br />\nPART 1<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=vcIWQdZlbKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fedit%3Fo%3DU%26video_id%3DvcIWQdZlbKE&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1793ce60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=vcIWQdZlbKE</a><br />\n<br />\nPART 2<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=3e6ESTeR3Fc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fedit%3Fo%3DU%26video_id%3D3e6ESTeR3Fc&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3aef504a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=3e6ESTeR3Fc</a><br />\n<br />\n做法如下:<br />\n<br />\n材料<br />\n法包一個<br />\n酸瓜切片數塊<br />\n美國辣肉腸1條<br />\n蘑菇切片<br />\n蛋黃醬<br />\n黑胡椒少許<br />\n蒜蓉少許<br />\n<br />\n第一部份: 焗法包<br />\n <br />\n1. 岩岩買番黎既法包, 好多時都唔脆, 可以用我既方法整脆佢. 哩個做法係方便屋企冇焗爐既朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐵獲落鹽1包, 鋪平, 最好粗鹽, 開中火襟蓋燒熱, 然後轉細火, 共3分鐘<br />\n<br />\n2. 放法包在鹽上面先焗一邊3分鐘. 鹽可以避免用火將獲直接空燒, 又可以製做一個平面, 令包受熱更平均.<br />\n<br />\n3. 反轉法包焗3分鐘.<br />\n<br />\n4. 拎出法包, 小心熱, 撥走D鹽, 哩個時候舊法包又香又脆.<br />\n<br />\n5. 中間開條坑, 預備放料.<br />\n<br />\n第二部份: 整餡 (其實第一部份應該同第二部份一齊做, 包焗好, 餡又岩岩做好, 然後再將佢地夾埋一齊, 咁個完成品就會好軟熟好脆. 但本癲狗拍片果陣忘記左做哩樣野, 我焗完包然後再整餡, 令到個法包攤凍左, 雖然都脆, 但有D硬, 所以大家要注意番.<br />\n<br />\n1. 落油小火燒熱, 一邊落香腸煎, 另一邊落蒜蓉再黑椒爆香, 再落蘑菇炒熟, 其間可以贊少少水令蘑菇快熟D.<br />\n<br />\n2. 將酸瓜片, 炒蘑菇片先放入熱狗, 再放香腸, 最後吱蛋黃醬在香腸上面, 完成."},{"pid":"6f0fa1f1e6f44cb1afc7beb2124571ea7ff1ed35","tid":225124,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdeeb594d6fe670647f105c25739838eca226c1","tid":225124,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好中意食哩隻牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4bd5b47ceffab06d2137968b326cee23000ac6e","tid":225124,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:24:00.000Z","msg":"個包想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942739607384428d3aba14da4d307603fc049a32","tid":225124,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T14:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個包想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩問題"},{"pid":"c84ce4da162dd4f0eab5c45a83706a56d9258e44","tid":225124,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"補條link<br />\n<br />\nPART 1<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=vcIWQdZlbKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fedit%3Fo%3DU%26video_id%3DvcIWQdZlbKE&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=1793ce60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=vcIWQdZlbKE</a><br />\n<br />\nPART 2<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/edit?o=U&amp;video_id=3e6ESTeR3Fc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fedit%3Fo%3DU%26video_id%3D3e6ESTeR3Fc&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIv